Module nwalters.inventorytrackingsystemproject

Class ModifyAPartControllerScreen

java.lang.Object
nwalters.inventorytrackingsystemproject.ModifyAPartControllerScreen
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ModifyAPartControllerScreen extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This class opens up the ModifyAPartForm.fxml screen. This will allow the user to change input on the screen and allow the user to change info about the part.
